Notes :
Promotional CD for "The Slim Shady LP". Issued in 1999 and sent to only a few media partners. Most of the songs are different to what is on the Slim Shady LP. "Low Down, Dirty" is re-performed with updated vocals. Different beats on "No One's Iller", "Take The Whole World With Me", "As The World Turns" and "When Bad Meets Evil" (Also different vocals on this track)..discogs link :
